    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
            <p>Not published before <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>125500</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="a">
                    <ab>
                    <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>σαι</orig>
                    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ωι</orig>
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>νοις</orig>
                    <lb n="3a"/><space extent="3" unit="cm"/>
	               </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="b">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ροι</orig>
                        <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ς</orig>
                        <lb n="2a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Intraduisible.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Not usefully translatable.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
                <p>Intraducibile.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>لا يمكن ترجمته بشكل جيد</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>Although very fragmentary, this stone should have born at least two different public texts, like in other dossiers such as 
               <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr068200</ref> and followings. However this fragment cannot belong to the same stone.</p>
                <p>As to the layout, it is clearly intended so as to have no cutting inside words at the end of lines.</p>
	           <p>At the end of line a.1, there was probably a prescriptive infinitive.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
    </text>
